// Copy this file to the repo root as `go.work` to route
// google.golang.org/protobuf through the trendvidia fork for your local
// builds and CI, without adding a `replace` to the published go.mod.
//
//     cp docs/go.work.example go.work
//
// `go.work` is git-ignored (see .gitignore) so it never leaks into the
// published module. See docs/protobuf-fork.md for the full rationale.

go 1.25.0

use .

// Route google.golang.org/protobuf to the trendvidia fork, which adds
// SetUnsafe / AppendUnsafe / MapSetUnsafe on *dynamicpb.Message for the
// PXF/SBE unmarshal fast paths (see encoding/pxf/decode_fast.go).
//
// Keep this version in lockstep with the fork tag referenced elsewhere
// (currently v1.36.12); the fork tracks upstream's tags closely.
replace google.golang.org/protobuf => github.com/trendvidia/protobuf-go v1.36.12
